title: Qualcomm's Evolution of Autonomous Products
itunes:title: Qualcomm's Evolution of Autonomous Products
description:
Patrick Little, General Manager of Qualcomm Global Automotive, discusses auto innovations being unveiled at the Consumer Electronics Show, specifically in the self-driving space.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
